snippet.title: ACLU Emails EXPOSED! Amber Heard Caught Lying AGAIN!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is Caught Lying AGAIN! This time about the infamous op-ed she said she wrote for the Washington Post, which she and her legal team also said, wasn't about Johnny Depp. Well new emails with ACLU prove this was false. Not only was it clearly about Johnny Depp, but she didn't even write the article! How many times do we need to prove her LIES before more people take this issue serioulsy? #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
